    "rationale": "All three primary QoIs meet the pre-specified quantitative acceptance criterion (E/uval < 1.96; percentage difference < 10%). Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels; the single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the conservative nature of the single loading angle tested and the breadth of corroborating evidence. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level required for this Class II device submission.",
